      chunks {
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Swiggy MCP Server"
          }
          text: "Order food, groceries and more through intelligent MCP server integrations."
        }
      }
      chunks {
        position: 1
        markdown_chunk {
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_1
            text: "Swiggy MCP Server"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_2
            text: "Supported Features"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Swiggy Food"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Instamart"
          }
          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Dineout"
          }
          text: "### Swiggy Food\nFood you \360\237\247\241, on time\n\n**Restaurant Search** - Discover restaurants by cuisine, name, or dish\n\n**Menu Browsing** - Explore menus, prices, and item details\n\n**Cart Management** - Add items, customize orders, and view bill breakdown\n\n**Food Ordering** - Place orders seamlessly with order tracking support (currently supports COD only)\n\n---\n\n### Instamart\nGet groceries & more, delivered in mins!\n\n**Product Search** - Find products by name, category, or brand at your delivery location\n\n**Cart Management** - View cart items, pricing, and bill breakdown with detailed cost analysis\n\n**Order Placement** - Seamlessly checkout and place grocery orders with instant confirmation (currently supports COD only)\n\n---\n\n### Dineout\nReserve tables at your favorite restaurants instantly.\n\n**Restaurant Discovery** - Find nearby restaurants based on your location and preferences\n\n**Restaurant Details** - Browse through detailed menus with prices, ratings, and exclusive offers\n\n**Slot Availability** - Check available booking time slots for your preferred date\n\n**Table Booking** - Reserve tables instantly with seamless booking support (supports free bookings only)"
        }
      }
