    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFolpVg2QVDDeBldy4fHXSDWKAXHWB-CiJz4eAsuaeELsg8we_SP5bFPw5DFJgn-YvB4lt8WfTOPMgHT7r7-lhBr5Rh4-NOyRY2GRPH0acsVTwq9cX_MY6uUGxdYS2S7Y0VfGD6TMWnN8cQHalbwno9oG3_BZl3YrIIDRD6WsExd4yt3HAhMfz4wfRFxt4Y6B1oOT2O9DC1Xy4Y8-G8X21VT6yjNp1txovWeMm7kkT90zun47Eqw1GHnUJ-0ROw45tiUPtL2ZtX"
      title: "medium.com"
    }
    summary: "\"Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest\" refers to a public GitHub repository maintained by Swiggy[1][2]. This repository is associated with Swiggy\'s Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers, an initiative that enables AI systems and chatbots to interact with Swiggy\'s services[3][4][5].\n\nThe Model Context Protocol (MCP) is an open-source framework that facilitates secure connections between AI tools and live data, sources, and services[3][5]. Swiggy has adopted MCP across its various platforms, including Swiggy Food, Instamart (for groceries), and Dineout (for restaurant reservations)[3][4][5][6]. This integration allows users to perform tasks like ordering food or groceries and booking tables through conversational AI agents such as ChatGPT and Google Gemini[3][4][5].\n\nThe `swiggy-mcp-server-manifest` GitHub repository likely serves as a resource for developers interested in building AI agents, applications, and other integrations that leverage Swiggy\'s MCP APIs[7][6]. It contains information and tools relevant to connecting with Swiggy\'s MCP servers, which expose different sets of tools for food, Instamart, and Dineout services[8][6].\n\nSources:\n[1] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGDymlKlGFlTtlmqYq7NNSkINSp4XeFeYPP4kNWDwdEnJN1A_Vd5cTX_nQDW59QZsKqOYK9M1JI1JzAqevAr33tg_wka63l1ycIkBVnUUiQ-lbl4V0VU01-7FK8bWSyjoUFInoA48e3FVKHNMIr6KM=)\n[2] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF9KDQzsj-zaAVn7o2v89kAzKvsYy5hsOni-gCH5hueO2Gt_dwn0K8kQj1AGme9WF2RPPxlkFbdNV3XrwIpCdGJak3v9B44HcuU2inCZGUSP7qvQh8=)\n[3] [indiatimes.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEVSJPpGtYMLXUcCapdB8hL9nTSolTCKFi77Cl6JAxCM5YPdqO4LJIyRmdff029g6NJY_GEEwXHwvdu0pXRQqS1Ivk7i3UWh5mMIFbNMf7l0pQN9AcN1y1M2li3jIDdHNaIaat1j2IJqGXHhF9-vOfwss9J3W7O4CKTXR6QAAYfDng738pQg3ICc70jMbsfRmpUAj571JJehats2ZsQNANvzpeLV6coleTtVkjchaSkQKGGUGBCqen4CVZJ93c92Y3EP2pf5w==)\n[4] [croma.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGGvUBQRW9oh0ry9m_o29iJ_CKvIRwa3DqYNCEB-vTPD5_vzuvfDBrbX_SFM9JLd7ea0NXk_9AFl1H9xaNgjvUYltLx_n_9WDIEb9QbuXs_aO1tCFNyRTG9MJHI6oc6EWBBtGRYAeXnOROPdJWMRTfDzd8PSji_pZ2aQ8cCWfIeSt4c3zBjBAiv1A==)\n[5] [ndtv.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQESoGUJuy90fOFKjiVuOOsNv8laLrQrVd0TwbzDcuCaUOs-AvZhB76B2F92QkAtyykv4F7CygVl7e-a6XMBlhbWiZpQLz19x3QZEGx61bRfWFhFrRlD3069iiPlT9PM6dHAthq76_vYrwq74bww5nxKJ9-HS9nDUPP1vUku2SwGYbwmlah89N9GTuRT503CnTlx5P-pvTEVX28FyrKjVPPGaQx4w8HPFwQFekoJaw6s6plqvw==)\n[6] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEOBZgim8Q9BEKYgmC5Judd4iTzmiP85rZKbB2KOqSzpGSuzqf_HTK2DEtfu48JauntCgjHO31uvtQwh_1awSnMy3dbu2J9mbrCQ7N5YfZrDHhE371tURPVY-jB86wNL9Nv5ZfEvQdxNNOU6XJFIEgUqlARYaHWisrD)\n[7] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFtI-5vwpSMJgWhgnVqnBzBVG5aTzV8rId3gy6NRlL4I7NJDn1FLkeyA-7ooBIahvSw49RYrH1VALafrxGWsYZ4Z9WWvb0RawFCWry0Bq5-rXegjqN0rHLygHEe)\n[8] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFolpVg2QVDDeBldy4fHXSDWKAXHWB-CiJz4eAsuaeELsg8we_SP5bFPw5DFJgn-YvB4lt8WfTOPMgHT7r7-lhBr5Rh4-NOyRY2GRPH0acsVTwq9cX_MY6uUGxdYS2S7Y0VfGD6TMWnN8cQHalbwno9oG3_BZl3YrIIDRD6WsExd4yt3HAhMfz4wfRFxt4Y6B1oOT2O9DC1Xy4Y8-G8X21VT6yjNp1txovWeMm7kkT90zun47Eqw1GHnUJ-0ROw45tiUPtL2ZtX)"
