    summary: "A search for files containing \"openapi,\" \"yaml,\" or \"json\" within the `github.com/Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest` repository did not yield direct results identifying specific files in the repository.\n\nHowever, general information regarding OpenAPI Specifications and its compatibility with YAML and JSON formats was found:\n\n*   The OpenAPI Specification (OAS) supports both YAML and JSON equally, treating them as interchangeable formats for describing HTTP APIs. An OpenAPI description is fundamentally a JSON object, regardless of whether it uses a `.json` or `.yaml` extension.[1][2][3]\n*   YAML is often favored for its human readability, support for comments, and ease of manual editing due to its indentation-based structure.[1]\n*   JSON is characterized by faster parsing, stricter syntax, and is generally more suitable for automation.[1]\n*   OpenAPI documents can be single JSON or YAML files, or they can be divided into multiple, connected parts.[4]\n*   It is recommended that the entry document for an OpenAPI Description be named `openapi.json` or `openapi.yaml`.[2][4]\n*   Some recommendations suggest using a multi-file YAML format for OpenAPI definitions, with the root document (e.g., `openapi.yaml`) containing the basic structure and referencing other files for paths and schema descriptions.[5]\n\nSources:\n[1] [dreamfactory.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG5udKshTmQ6a42q3Yf_5anQ0gMZWOiu4CBKuNuzSljRyy0AIUPDUKsPS_ZisMgq0obaXcyaSXFMIGGFMJ8gLmp9zXc8WxM0GJPRK5UK_WqgeUmmpqQi2nq-Y3MiEhH15LMZjZi1mYeHh3UHiwdxKpemiCbJNMH6knFvo7C5QE352FDzzUIzQ==)\n[2] [openapis.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaXCjQUUSOImYaiVHccRAahIO9tM0Dx6OuunHSXQip0Vl-udXp4o2WwUAUwLDaig-uioI6tjWsuSWa5C-E1x2aSjGATgu-ZQf_bLO2GNbCYm7X8zJIdDhWIJlkEj1a7lJTK3Hq)\n[3] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9lYso9_a97xMQYJhEfpYNm0_lEWmyd-4zhEiWnOGQEJyKHMe77SE-aCjag0IZ193i8cBF9GudnpFP8YYWZJkxrbmnQD0gCcJr7-Iej6McSr9mO6g_TY2gqGe1dAvLNlFjA9y30ZZYsbCki8MnKkYX1HuZDApi4i8GcdFfjC_skRGe4NOZE_EitJYcfv2uVZVRoIgh8cldOyiBgfV_XEmMAl0NtoXlzCtNdtUteRbSnUzahMzN)\n[4] [swagger.io](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEix4PC81eo3abDU9Ia8WgQxIfRubMKzb_jyRKL33SQtUW0OwNPrK4nmRLKE30XumJfYYHj1KKf_SmUtEbsBbBoOWDqtKrRvS9MQIPsRMcA1ThoKQWMDD-nylFxhw==)\n[5] [redocly.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGqPvmRhSbASOaeKBL8Xdj8w7ff5Q2iBmeZ6WP8wqYb6X3T4FdUuGhgxLblfvXKSMfAl2ym4tb-l3CvZGb2aXb2HDrlTnKZSbJhP2j38ZR0jvls7Dlsl0ggDK9Mk2lIvtavvpEsgH0i6udjHH7W)"
