      title: "lobehub.com"
    }
    summary: "The \"Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest\" refers to a public GitHub repository that outlines the manifest for Swiggy\'s Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers[1][2][3][4]. This manifest describes the functionalities and endpoints of various Swiggy services exposed through the MCP.\n\n**Model Context Protocol (MCP)**\nThe Model Context Protocol (MCP) is a permission-based protocol that enables AI models to interact with Swiggy\'s services by invoking predefined tools[4]. It provides a standardized method for AI agents to access specific functionalities without direct access to Swiggy\'s internal databases or payment systems[2][4].\n\n**Instamart and MCP**\nSwiggy Instamart, the quick commerce arm of Swiggy, utilizes its own dedicated MCP server, accessible at `https://mcp.swiggy.com/im`[2][3][5][6]. Instamart was the first quick-commerce platform globally to adopt the MCP[6]. This server exposes a range of tools, including:\n*   Product search[3][5]\n*   Cart management (view, update, clear)[3][5]\n*   Order placement and tracking[3][5]\n*   Delivery address management (create, delete, fetch)[5]\n*   Access to frequently ordered items[5]\n\n**Other Swiggy MCP Servers**\nIn addition to Instamart, Swiggy also provides MCP servers for its other core services:\n*   **Food**: Located at `https://mcp.swiggy.com/food`, offering tools for restaurant search, menu browsing, cart management, and food ordering[7][2][3][6].\n*   **Dineout**: Accessible at `https://mcp.swiggy.com/dineout`, with tools for restaurant discovery, viewing details, checking slot availability, and table booking[7][2][3][6].\n\n**Usage and Limitations**\nThe MCP allows integration with various AI platforms and tools, such as Claude Desktop, VS Code Copilot, and Cursor[2][3][4]. A community-built command-line interface, `swiggy-cli`, also exists to interact with these MCP servers[1].\n\nHowever, there are important limitations:\n*   Third-party app development through MCP is currently not permitted due to ongoing security and compliance reviews[3].\n*   Users are advised against simultaneously opening the Swiggy mobile app and using MCP integrations to prevent potential session conflicts[3].\n*   Cash on Delivery (COD) orders placed via MCP cannot be canceled[3].\n\nSources:\n[1] [jsdelivr.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFIvblZpb-_EVasoBQp8mq7_dgSkPEA2ScRv8CvIhD88CAbcRkYDpujnSGC1KKlfRpCvV5fYvQOC-42xFLtTEGonyRhna0YTkYFemtppUOoWrMTx0SMWrR7vBCFNBzYi1dyl2GAY9xOTXyw)\n[2] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH1GxDV70jb_hFPZbZYNcLE6xg7nXJhf8VWoMmCstMcjkV9C6i_kLJq2Nk-50gIGXC-iQ7AXOOZLxAP3dezZRsSu1E-V1ZgR6l5206opzHVWIvBM0Y7x1i_uN_oXNkWZbpqT-44vBY5l8dUyA==)\n[3] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGqXjxUxATqRSOQOe_mPoTMssji4wd5PO3dZ8Y8APK6WqxxtGgu8pqa9RVWABxX5HmsIk0mn4ra8oHTz1YhN8-SDwx1q8uDKmu9YC9npRZ4Eg0MwTP6bPv9JzEaJh_NGGK5alIbMmSUV-y1ysagd4Y=)\n[4] [youtube.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGYBr95FiRGQazgMGqGKjEJQPmhDZOUNPd0r0XTKPmVZ74UzuPlrZytQT0XfOQ0q3zL3cc38tnv5tD1xZhdS5B3-OS1OlDvOJpzb3mWy2XOQ4md1ymRbdskKiyytxWuyxq3G0WkBU4=)\n[5] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGXDummxUYzzuPKWjHMJrcTs33-XA_LoaLsT2-SYd4AxwQPfNzfwHN2E8kDwNG8BLh0jb9on7nFuAiPm_mxQcKFCs9p_7pDE1Mt44cjehSTnsE9q5uTW8uc1DfYmHg1mMmaUg2v_x0lr9h3iLj8iZdHbBTfhg==)\n[6] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHpTeQSNh7JxbcCn4joaQuPHu8Zeb7pUJZ0QfLDUJdYxv5ouUY8XVFuKQWfMYFvqLLrJ72-Af7dIxBaZ4lKEUBP1al8GlD9a6Pbkexl3wvdNsSzWXxCBNmQALv9QeZWBvUZt8bkkN1MXfvaMJ5hhzIyBAPk1HH57YtmUYn4Mir-Ab1xTPj6TIGT3247q7GEUJmK1YWp7Odj9ORzT0LkSjkS7_efwWOTUgzZKQnuuDIAIDwdCWL5wHzI1XieSRUK8GeEWDQIXVPd)\n[7] [lobehub.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQElEsjDUtIMyXoPRgvVhDkVWGACYyi1NRzOOLSbEp4MOKNz1c5dz57tDHg8JsyirT784UngwynWdaJCDP2i3PI8nA8u1W5tn9a9gQKqUtGTj5_XnmlS-pmSLZy_PRKWy2B0CNKfs8GdSfmr60kCb070YmpJidk_LP2bZiqoxvwIBjxF_WmEGWGzAg==)"
    search_type: SEARCH_WEB_TYPE_WEB
  }
}
