      title: "claude.com"
    }
    summary: "The search for \"mcp\", \"json\", or \"yaml\" within the `github.com/Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest` domain reveals information primarily related to the Model Context Protocol (MCP) and its configuration.\n\nThe Model Context Protocol (MCP) is an open standard designed to connect AI applications, such as large language models (LLMs), with external tools and services[1][2][3]. It facilitates communication between AI models and external systems like databases and web services, allowing LLMs to access real-time data and perform actions[2][3].\n\nConfiguration of MCP servers is frequently handled through `mcp.json` files[1][4][5]. These JSON files can be used to manually configure MCP servers and are often found in a project\'s `.vscode/mcp.json` directory or a user\'s profile to enable sharing of server configurations[1]. The `mcp.json` file can contain a JSON block specifying server details[4]. The communication between an MCP client and server primarily relies on JSON-RPC 2.0 messages, indicating a significant role for JSON in the protocol\'s transport layer[2].\n\nWhile the search query included \"yaml\", direct instances of `.yaml` files within the `Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest` repository were not explicitly returned. However, a `.goreleaser.yaml` file was mentioned in documentation related to a \"GitHub MCP Server,\" suggesting that YAML files can be present in projects associated with MCP servers[4].\n\nSources:\n[1] [visualstudio.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHWu4rtkHkFiS1s1wh3k1XiNPUKsLZThj1DU9Y0RGdIki47SFklkt7hkjFnjFbug2Vkx3LoED_Ulnqit521bXjUYOKovgO6o7O5fdWpcita-VJ5_xgxSnvYZevFslgs7o1Z-W5I7V407Qfq6b6GDLtW9ZZhuOWFaL3lPcF0uds=)\n[2] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF1mZYaqvrWbJprkHd1c2Ek0iHVBafrM71KkA4Qb0lz7eM_iXE7wwGl6XXkFwOFx4gf4IqxqrmtZxRRHp_HtklfucKoZqwhnk19VMzoUwsbwoaf4R14n1xWi_JbwzBZopZl9Db6qbbJfRRs1vCzZ-bkob4l4tIuqh4iyw==)\n[3] [modelcontextprotocol.io](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF6ACr_gJGyejJr69_lJDThKfqJHrOMG2fhJGcRgzMdtnHu454yeVg8FSBGZN72TkunhiLNLpjXZrUp26lPFwR8rNU4QNFnUwAznBHSpG4TRYUwnNgZfggpZcNBEz6UQgg4_FAbIUY4XcY4jifqpdIHCMy2qA==)\n[4] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEEXqGhvzSG3ht26VL9VukArmZL-9g1c6IuRn1Z85c6mG0rfkUxlTtONloPAZ8CADscKdzRjcRzc1RQYWZFAmZDDNz8-qWTcJrXuvQQ9qAYX5_k-9zkNeALiG6EDJVJu4NAUDwq4w==)\n[5] [claude.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHFb0cH1PT5iOrl8aUQaxU8eF0lvtVMM-g4Jl9lQI8HElln6lom338bN7-Tw2v9Dq3W7eh1srLKahh_0T7zx89THAMBS-eaTVQxH_VkGpv_Yb9mQENkm00eA-Hlcv4=)"
