    summary: "Swiggy utilizes a \"Model Context Protocol\" (MCP) server architecture, referred to as \"swiggy-mcp-server-manifest\", to expose its commerce platform for Food, Instamart, and Dineout services through a Builders Club initiative[1][2]. These MCP servers provide APIs for developers, startups, and enterprises to build AI agents, apps, and integrations[1].\n\nThe URLs for the Swiggy MCP servers are:\n*   **Food:** `https://mcp.swiggy.com/food`[3][4]\n*   **Instamart:** `https://mcp.swiggy.com/im`[3][4]\n*   **Dineout:** `https://mcp.swiggy.com/dineout`[3][4]\n\nEach of these servers offers a suite of API tools:\n*   **Food MCP Server** provides tools for restaurant search, menu browsing, cart management, and food ordering[3][5].\n*   **Instamart MCP Server** includes tools for product search, cart management, and order placement for groceries and essentials[6][3].\n*   **Dineout MCP Server** offers functionalities for restaurant discovery, checking slot availability, and table booking[7][3].\n\nThe API schema for these tools is designed to be understood by AI agents, allowing them to dynamically discover and interact with various Swiggy services[2]. Authentication for these MCP servers is handled via OAuth 2.1 with PKCE[2][3][8].\n\nSources:\n[1] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHdT5OSRGCG16QU3jQymSIBsa8iGXZW1M-VlHGDK9a1XPQpp06lxViK2dtKDjsbr6A8pfjlZpndBr-DjRILm1-Oc3aqsMit3biq_EDtH3xWA0_dr8HEhGgNBAs=)\n[2] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFghU2WJvQe105gB1tTLV2QZFDad0AhbreCJBc4j_eSvLqaoBXXWf6hDKzsmHCkhiDC6b-CAJav9p0vglgk3xTu90B8RLkfgUF2CokHU1PQh4M4_mv8x5dxkStUt3IDTlenyfa_fm9cZoxZ9Y9WLv8dA3wgasdpFKk=)\n[3] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHjUEQ_8fycIx-MlAtbkDcEDITjcZ92Z2iF2lPo18CkgQk5RZWU_uVEoT274d647weDDxAj7YkNChemmCHfYIZY9PTNU57sRhW0T8tv4HVetaoyl2CMk_QG0LeZYxLO1dnokFVLUVvzAfhgPlzoZg==)\n[4] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFUBJJp9Zg6P0uSwEdAYwG7kvLkj3i-Vgw5YlJBnUXg-Wn4aiwYFQ9I3oCQX7OmyaxkiCn8CHMyWWtBOgsCYhegpP9ofFg3w5sDuug5xR4M7hDL_zboIlod6NFb3RO2QUHfFGMAK4z_x3Qr7-LeOsXpFV2w6ID9wH4F7pkI_L3fqMvpwWX8FCfAmveitGM5GQ-z26GCXNFhZE4eqIUj1pEkZ3dHezKOkHHwScvVLdpplt-3x1yplWxr7rV0g6E4Uvm1TBYe3p0=)\n[5] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_RdV6GbX2M3kJMKrRVgRnmaQYa4xxSVMzoWt36Lfr5V2hGh3VdCYJoHA9D8WJuxwp4iw-_3ZOwtmRWwn00SHwNMg-KTgZyTslWEzTA4E5WIz8LbQstVf--nZe-ciHhGbBPyQnghzGcEVtQ8cA7A==)\n[6] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFjg0lbZ5QpJk2fT8I671gBCgWemdO79-VSv6uAUlZfqqxQei3yfG9o90Ej1xkncI3B5alWolA4ZDYGW2e49Z0YfjqAuQgyUZ6DH2xaqz5fPlcyi_9RX01f_tvmIkt4Uk0OpJ0y9DKMsLewgljBtXreJayL)\n[7] [apify.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHFQPx5qFReG0dw-pAa01y0tr96kTcgNsPMKjLaIbnVmnaW_hP2xfBCQxhPSUMCoagPR3DPrIm7LOJT1GaySssb8zcgi_t8fWASIsGqsy2S_Z5T6a1QKrnMmksvxmeqMw9UXBPmdwgYYFJ9lZYDgVPAFe1aW-fghrM6JwiDqQ==)\n[8] [jsdelivr.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF116Z-ywqfcp7_58DbA97OI1ndKkkvIjx-TWBaJmCRlW9MfYTpBg7dBzE10DxvAwI9qq1v0D8vgC2AfAeOjOKYB3fZHfrONEX28eB_FLfBO9tRkayfU3RLFN4uD0CCykC1LmLreR66Bh0=)"
