    }
    summary: "The \"swiggy-mcp-server-manifest\" refers to the configuration and tools exposed by Swiggy\'s Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers, which allow AI agents and other external clients to interact with Swiggy\'s commerce platform, including Instamart[1][2][3][4].\n\n### Swiggy Instamart MCP Workflow and Details\n\nSwiggy Instamart functions as an AI-powered grocery and essentials shopping assistant through its MCP server[5][6]. The workflow involves an AI agent selecting a tool from the Instamart server\'s catalog, sending a JSON-RPC call to the Instamart endpoint, and receiving a processed result[3][7].\n\nKey details of the Swiggy Instamart MCP integration include:\n*   **Endpoint**: The specific HTTP endpoint for the Instamart MCP server is `https://mcp.swiggy.com/im`[2][5][3][6][8].\n*   **Protocol**: It utilizes the Model Context Protocol (MCP), an open standard for AI agents to communicate with external tools[3].\n*   **Authentication**: Access is managed through standard OAuth 2.1 with PKCE, which involves whitelisted redirect URIs and Bearer tokens[2][3][9][6][7].\n*   **Use Case**: This integration is designed for agent developers building with various AI SDKs (e.g., OpenAI Agents SDK, Anthropic SDK) and for AI-client users of platforms like Claude Desktop, ChatGPT, and VS Code, enabling them to integrate Swiggy\'s services as tools[3][6][7].\n*   **Limitations**: Currently, third-party app development is restricted due to ongoing security reviews. Users are also advised not to use the Swiggy mobile app simultaneously with MCP integrations to prevent session conflicts. Orders placed via MCP using Cash on Delivery (COD) cannot be canceled through the API[2][9].\n\n### Swiggy Instamart MCP Tools List\n\nThe Swiggy Instamart MCP server exposes 13 distinct tools, categorized into Discover, Cart, Order, and Track stages to facilitate various grocery shopping functionalities[5][3][6][8].\n\n**Discover Tools**:\n*   `create_address`: To add a new delivery address for the user[5].\n*   `delete_address`: To remove a saved delivery address[5].\n*   `get_addresses`: To retrieve all saved delivery addresses, sorted by the last order date[5].\n*   `search_products`: To find products available at a specified address, including variants like different pack sizes or quantities[5].\n*   `your_go_to_items`: To fetch frequently or recently ordered items for a given delivery address[5].\n\n**Cart Tools**:\n*   `clear_cart`: To remove all items from the Instamart cart[5].\n*   `get_cart`: To retrieve the current Instamart grocery cart, including all items and a bill breakdown[5].\n*   `update_cart`: To modify the Instamart grocery cart by replacing its entire contents with provided items[5].\n\n**Order Tools**:\n*   `checkout`: To place and confirm a Swiggy Instamart grocery order, handling both order creation and payment confirmation in a single operation[5].\n\n**Track Tools**:\n*   `get_order_details`: To obtain detailed information for a specific Instamart order using its order ID[5].\n*   `get_orders`: To fetch the user\'s Instamart order history or past order preferences[5].\n*   `track_order`: To monitor the real-time status of a Swiggy Instamart order[5].\n\n**Support Tools**:\n*   `report_error`: To report an error within the system[5].\n\nSources:\n[1] [lobehub.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaJW008BVScurq1pji1TzPS1U5f9eXflZmugAIPw_dqczVAYZrUXG-mJ1puz-rQSaE7_4oV3hgnzKGtkbhuXyeFUBIjfi_5BZh7k5dKIQN7CnbQMgkgH-55eIwO0t2xq5E1hQghkGC5-k3GraOfyNEzo88xkI6WXENQsjwUMVREv02fi5BbjWyOw==)\n[2] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEHsMB68aNLHMu_Qb2FHYrvuoOqf1DDZHOy3OSDftQTnXqfR2oR2cD9GcpvDP4j1El74vS0ObKizJYTjFa006j-lcSmnSnSJrImhV8LdMs_mgjuKqul-4VX7Q5LRcEvz2P991JyVp76b9engMt7eGc=)\n[3] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHVAUxlB9LgnGt_u3mxG3SE9PaY36j7Z6T4dkFqCODMkPb_8kbmO6_Fb4jwVHoZxd219MX1TfdlU69VFT2gJXHRFlVWCnlNxbC9nST7XSAFdq_erNicD4mtSyO7eGM5n1m-8H9Ehl8KSHFXSH7AIrm2LRuWKK7Hdplg)\n[4] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGcspcVtZ4Wb8fx_543yJS4yAVC7810EvF04OExYvPUS5wjF_WtECVqaSK8HYRM5bQ7XTK3s_UoaosO8FvRrGWdv39yQ061U55ZD9Q1jECz87Gnq7E=)\n[5] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9MUvDZBjTUR1bGtkx9pBsdloKkLQZbSJM-0ycDY-NXIs6K5SaRXPnPqqAOm8gTLwQpqXgSPcLKmxC1Q3AqXjMal-9Sb2O4Eq4IzjYyiPNTx_hx-PbhAwf8LP-zVxtuBur0t6TmHBNzWB8OEYouFGikdARKw==)\n[6] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHthtulu0KoHmXt6vFe8o6RMOj3zgYa7Au3EYKgC4JPIzpPjMLF5ezcNWUwlf-qsigL0ZQyc3oWvVCGvfJIXZ5YZaLHvhjarNJL7OyUhBaaOyZtKAJq7BSaJjH21POmSCOiwLu5wNUtGxvn0Ma5TJPN6OsK_SK3u1PNns4Et1mugjwLQqsWjrn5UCVdPB8SfMGnoc2kCfTPCSawioXFSBavMz7T7iGyik4C1FeiviutKrIs2A0DwZEmDschI6UpOyMDqX3c4yLY)\n[7] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGv8xF3Wi-zPmCV2xPvC-63nUCE6Crq_VnEXoqYAys6Cw-C_IP5HFZV8N1OHzSm-7um254wxmjGK7g3ynLOoSp-9V_EjI3JsuoLfL-pLwfEOXyZOkA_WUZnMda8VthGCoOhXQFx7tOHbSGOuDeA-GwT)\n[8] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn_GpGAWFgAOD8x1XNcV6oTCj2t06m5kAv8Lzhb2tXtOovFofotailEe13IQny1mkTaIhBxUy4jA8XHAgyi38FTwYV_S_ifyqGYfwM8VYLWbbotJ_BxQLRGnt3UGdQiUsgK-ZVgQ-oRCFW)\n[9] [jsdelivr.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGi1Rb7YLYqBnC4NemMCx_d71hJKXdTOWgcSU6HLiiEz9EZCd3Wv39sxVQPNUQuElcJMBYszkHjhdiZQBgwRpvYYAjSMUZkIv74yPl2uHwpwcaJGL8oTTh5KH_6avXRssROXACVMlWiOp21)"
