      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHSTGzMbtEv4ctV48jIoVJIFELEwc6IOPXR2cclbz44VkZaJDxhtP_0_Gir7eHIb7BvFvGBauly3zEYJoTa6LRiU_o-JQxDH2FfkLGXMXKJe1rgwt0BspU9s28otDNLcJslAl9MBTWgnaKeRqYMFmTPgTQstf8DP9w1DB9y3CzsJTznCTle-RD0KTwlz2UrAidv5MRDPdC9"
      title: "fooddatascrape.com"
    }
    summary: "Swiggy has opened its commerce platform through the \"Swiggy Builders Club,\" exposing its APIs via Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers, an open standard for AI agents to interact with external tools[1][2][3].\n\nKey aspects of Swiggy\'s API offerings include:\n*   **MCP Servers** Swiggy offers three distinct MCP servers:\n    *   **Food** (mcp.swiggy.com/food) provides 14 tools for restaurant discovery, menus, ordering, and tracking[1][3][4].\n    *   **Instamart** (mcp.swiggy.com/im) offers 13 tools for quick-commerce grocery services[1][3][4].\n    *   **Dineout** (mcp.swiggy.com/dineout) includes 8 tools for table reservations[1][3][4].\n*   **API Specifications** Swiggy\'s API landscape involves standard specifications:\n    *   Unofficial Swiggy API specifications, including those for Instamart, Orders, and Profile APIs, are available in OpenAPI (OAS3) format, often as YAML files[5][6].\n    *   Third-party platforms like Apify provide downloadable OpenAPI definitions in JSON format for Swiggy Restaurant Menu Extractor and Swiggy Scraper[7][8].\n    *   The MCP servers expose tool schemas that AI agents can utilize[1][4]. Additionally, third-party APIs interfacing with Swiggy often use RESTful APIs with JSON responses[9].\n*   **Authentication** Access to Swiggy\'s MCP APIs uses standard OAuth 2.1 with PKCE[1][4]. General API integration typically requires API keys, obtainable through the Swiggy Developer Portal[10][11].\n*   **Purpose and Use Cases** These APIs are designed to enable developers to build AI agents, conversational commerce solutions, and applications for seamless food ordering, grocery stocking, and table reservations by integrating with Swiggy\'s live infrastructure[1][2][3].\n*   **Availability** The official Swiggy Builders Club and MCP are currently available for an India-only user base, with production access being invite-based[1].\n\nSources:\n[1] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFzQkzguUC9HpBlbwjQcnBblkYvh-79rx4IUxJFKv6_B_INNf3HsA2ygw5WXDk4_LOI0bfavhbf_QpJvoCj1-kpDg3IvEvNfNxIZSvYAl-4cR7E62MSlLgP_zNmfih-gFVXPTwnd8ntuaPhqUTxqMAlJGOZJVOnaD8X)\n[2] [youtube.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEfVnIPxN6QNshbArHgKe8aTBwtzoCRaThlPdHtN7Jx3Jbc38ddfmE4ZEpCWpZ1jZy87GfZhKyoQSsAUYST3VTsuQ8FZKeOvY964vBfaqZBiqFuLYzchn-o-APGmnnsLEsYkQ0T4w==)\n[3] [swiggy.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEa_lgbf5v4fNvXW4qAtmJTH6W-LPS-FykdI4Vr944OdMRuD9qoLW0gRlsb6qJZngEuzCTCPANe61hZtIEhj0nsqfujvWIJYF3o_UrCUNCyvWLCXxhYgNXf6uW9)\n[4] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHD82ByWL6I70Z_V4MWo6hVhHeaDnPXnwuxnpwHZ-rEJeFP3EiIKs3jBiNMguES8TQhd9L_Ej9USsbhQ8jp5L03CyrfrFprT-Q9HAE90E1D0TUvq0e0Npl1ch6zRdikksT_NvJjoQaiwTDPWdMuX_pNaGcaylqqcZiJgOd0VGHNke8HqqghNBleVDxh-YYeOvUl0jIkvZVFElgjUxQA0xK3uMQDVUt1THlnpJ4LtNWend6OC8LBefy3pWsduREhse6mFHl4eLKR)\n[5] [captnemo.in](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHmp5STZMt4rFnaEl37e8sDnrsKETz61atSnAWyytTnlGM7z-XBaP--mQZrOzHgL6f4DV-XI7EN0e7Zu96mb6qPDldiLBMfbbmysJFy8nkGjW-LAbQfURD-RFb6v2gFQF8l0cTdEQMuwoFNqwOQ08mI7kV6IAWMPLbycjgvop-78unalJ_bkg==)\n[6] [captnemo.in](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFcy3TXrJAbR27ua94WOtFmGQHO2h5tL-kzvEkUDQEk9Uc_iKgBl7dOScPbZB7bQ9YVdEp-H9jxfR8swkdNZbDDGLqJT74yvqLvorzpjiFqKjBmPDWM4DrurvZdmSZznk2c_qk-W4F1y5d-cg==)\n[7] [apify.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH4KHSvhpZpuasab7x0E860b3MxlQk5GuzDjSsyZsLnb-nfiSm9etivnfnAnHoE34W81tfl02CiNmx8Ud_m1mqfN1Y1KlX4P4YmBfyUi-16dLxB4QqHHXS1R_42n2rlu75qQiOBTSIcH6xvvt6bYCGaXWLMS7NDSFbK2Lr00VJ8rJl2)\n[8] [apify.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEQiVs9hoP_-pB6vWkCgSEnjvZCx9zXHuxVWglbq3XwLTuy5p74ecrXuQI0s08AOQcYeB99V7uJzFNAo5JCz51CQSc9Io3gRQQ9oj06W38nz5W4EOFSCbMVIPX3-7Dao6nsXRBzray78BMThmJ9Dlr6nNI=)\n[9] [nextract.dev](https