    summary: "A search for \"Swiggy\" within the domain \"captnemo.in\" did not yield any specific results from that domain. The search results provided general information about Swiggy, an Indian online food ordering and delivery company. Swiggy, headquartered in Bengaluru, was founded in 2014 and operates food delivery services in over 700 Indian cities and quick-commerce services (Instamart) in 100 cities as of 2025[1][2].\n\nSwiggy functions as a hyperlocal delivery and on-demand logistics platform, connecting customers, restaurants, stores, and delivery partners through its app[1]. Beyond food delivery, Swiggy has expanded its services to include Swiggy Instamart for instant grocery delivery and Swiggy Genie for pick-up and drop logistics[1]. They also offer Swiggy Bolt for ultra-fast food delivery in select areas and \"Scenes\" for events and ticketing[1][2]. In 2022, Swiggy acquired the dining and table reservation platform Dineout[2]. Swiggy also provides an IRCTC delivery service, allowing users to order food on trains[3].\n\nSources:\n[1] [appsrhino.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGsZ1X0-gCiXY3HPZ9mZYeMSmIvslEWMzi6cR-O2urj0YcGNKTIKyonDiwfsNIBDSFoTxI-rIUHlsgWxTVFiz0Lrnu4RSBrqaPC3HLeiZMKczx6tgOqAQrLw-HnXCZeiFyKSTcQuy8rrPXeh1J7Z5iIz_72gceRXGyfYFjwZdY=)\n[2] [wikipedia.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGpGKZZCuhPWeeYuvqDh1ExxSgzStMjHzvyadSp7REdgU5_vHvd3ZIfYIEDVqGVJ55nRbd8PaZ_fgczcDCgsm47Z_Z8XQLwJjKjaMAS_OO27UVEq3u5DDclw8mUwo0iMw==)\n[3] [apple.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEqI2SPpSihExQTd9q8e73nEd5vSR7WQ0OPo86HxzIEkwfJEf5PJO0JQcOqDU6pJIgWoAUtMyr7O902IBnoqY68rP1sAc6edEmyQAuUbYTOs-cneHbGJD-fsFRQWNS0n1ckcEHaS0vBqSSDp-PWWg09CCzu_4xzpJQje1Pae7IIDogO)"
