    summary: "I couldn\'t find any direct search results specifically for \"README.md\" or \"Getting Started\" within the `github.com/Swiggy/swiggy-mcp-server-manifest` repository. The search results provided general information about what `README.md` files are[1][2][3] and the common meaning of the phrase \"Getting Started\"[4][5].\n\nA `README.md` file is a crucial document in a repository that explains the project\'s purpose, setup, and usage, often formatted using Markdown[1][3]. Platforms like GitHub automatically display this file on a project\'s homepage if it\'s located at the root of the repository[6].\n\nSources:\n[1] [geeksforgeeks.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFx3QVvBl0LjQQmOiJRkFO6RWlzlRJHrH9EiayPADJcLWyVDmyWtQE8v9f9YyIdiTuEemqhIihGpWHc-yKhqx49CUUhbL5B6aNIFrtZDTvGTF7xafvexgQrt35Dml_3oyOJwQcHijZDQKn2_zv73HqCuy2y)\n[2] [versent.com.au](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE7QgW6yD4YfMqnzpi4qjmA7froFr3X1p7ampBEefXNGLsYtHT3X7qwe44Wx2qT668df3RFNDXqA5-4zjpsPTpLYJUeU7-_-bbfQ3SFXTpeL8m83FzrMJARQRlgUIdhCko49l5-kOcgc0t4F1iv8q0bf1LCIw==)\n[3] [markdown.land](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEbRP1gnMsqqCNNZhIq_Th0QXD1brQjpPfX3yIWl09sMEYKmG1lWv_uiTB2PR_LEtTSkEsb_swjKAESPSde6iUp_mFo-CMBJV9HjaeB4VNBi5Ef0m0ORzCOdQ==)\n[4] [wikipedia.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGTNEuKInrkD6sbKbst8TvTvd2F-FWfO5O_BcF1qaxdYZ7bARewEyXHRS3SmImD88-TIuDNaL4dEKUGA6mZNgYUYKatPPqbxXx2Ancc5muNFYYkkxykNFM86m4aY1azu7pP1XPQPSu1)\n[5] [merriam-webster.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEbPnPPMCIQC8WaU1q1LBUesaxUoWoJCdjzKECnU9CV2LRWreJVMO-xwqTXo6-wb6VPARwZN8kVI-gZrtEcFQ1dImmUxWxYwYAQF-PUNIDSjGfX0NWQeJPkCXrxf6YW0pdd4jdI8tX7N7Hc6S3hyWUtej0=)\n[6] [youtube.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaziOCM_dY9JXRRzC-R4yP_DqiDR6SoXv2FyIDnUBzDzqclYf6DOa9Ev9StHqnCsT5GsbkIHeTdGBEwGf66m