      title: "reddit.com"
    }
    summary: "Swiggy is an Indian online food ordering and delivery company, headquartered in Bengaluru, that also offers quick-commerce services under the name Instamart. The company, incorporated in 2013, operates food delivery services in over 700 Indian cities and Instamart in 100 cities as of 2025[1].\n\nInstamart, launched by Swiggy in August 2020, provides instant grocery delivery using a network of dark stores[1]. While Swiggy Stores were closed in early 2021, Instamart expanded its operations[1]. Instamart delivers groceries, emergency supplies, midnight cravings, and more, offering a wide range of products including fresh produce, dairy, snacks, personal care items, and baby care products[2][3]. It operates from 6 a.m. to late at night in over 120 cities, though specific timings may vary by city due to government regulations[3].\n\nSwiggy and Instamart offer various features, including no minimum order conditions for food delivery, real-time order status updates, and multiple payment options[2][3]. Swiggy One users receive unlimited free delivery on both food and Instamart orders[2]. Swiggy has also introduced an IRCTC delivery service, allowing users to order food on trains[2][3].\n\nIn the quick-commerce market, Instamart ranks behind competitors like Blinkit and Zepto in terms of market share[1]. In 2025, Blinkit, a unit of Zomato\'s parent Eternal Ltd., outpaced Swiggy\'s Instamart in order volumes and revenue projections[4]. Blinkit\'s dark store network and average order value are also projected to be higher than Instamart\'s in 2026[4]. There was a discussion in January 2025 about Swiggy potentially launching Instamart as a separate app, although it had previously attempted this[5].\n\nSources:\n[1] [wikipedia.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG-na_wJnYqZ2tRkp6vuGmXukGkXEcnuAWr8la-XXRQ6ixkc_HfO2vL0GhIHtt6QdoY1U6wiyBc0LZFkiXHNayng5iA6d3_QD5yt2fIs61O5y8YdVJc5C0wwqQalYs5)\n[2] [apple.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENsexnuLGFt3sHjmBWkdSyEsUmmVz0jUc-Ccf6mXp8aS0oDLhMMZVreOP4khHOqyAIGxEMM2UfgKswvXa1CJB2Ur5BLIdSoDUqF0l4mFAWlbngoXTsX7tGczIpirV3bZ1CwRlEmoFPuSPvbxpeklaQjRJi6uFP0h7aaaZRxSOX7DQ=)\n[3] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH6DrFJObiDWrYWf5RtXKWesWYpsuy0lzoCpQR18ygw1IDZIhzBCD1b-7BbqhpBetG0IKQB__lU58TetXC7kbDbEXjW2_DNcHEvaLT11YlKKapaItqVJydzlNf9vWBPbnaGwWkHZeKkMU-3ETrybG732ivqp-YAY_Zx)\n[4] [spglobal.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2TiEEEnVc_kdgQPIReQLyZvBo_Ka3hSjitKxv_JHpgc2UizydJy-CdE8Iu8GTz1Fh3wYZN9tU34KZhwjJxiA8jcv0-iFPEQsR3CPxZapF78Yj3se8z93cloVHDgEllfFNM4H8JHk_8EJOfW5z_8K6_rFumEAbSQbgPZoRcuHHVhN-VGLYtwP9IPeyRsbsvShMsiAZrgj5remeWLINutg4noKE2Ew3llXA_qRZqadyCKSvf5mO-cXEcygC2OUuZR8e2k2REKvFC9nh)\n[5] [reddit.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHIbgTfRY_sZ4coGeXeBfwwIrhjAj7v2Tfwc4R2xXtUDGWIr553hy1A4x8Zqwp6sdRGjy1UGDVWnDenps-3DShofh9cA3ql_cq2O-gmoSIjevG-8jpsBymfuPBQcbcrcPWY6WwLisSfsmFi1rTx3WMTqmKk-wTCu8u3LrN56W5Ez_5p17J_wg9foPR0FmvmVlODgGbYO9Rnx1SrjWFuOEMMVMPuFg==)"
    search_type: SEARCH_WEB_TYPE_WEB
  }
