    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHXNRKS-B3fDTxMfSTvxyF3BryMscdk6WNR9Isl42wFssaeEkqf2C6WNYIau0lhjTEgeD3hTTgAqGqCczHfzBpB32pHooKQOW9ZK7Sin70EUugUPZ8JjaOqLQUeHU3PuMlghvapzxehJlmpB_U1S85KFz3jCrSQYw=="
      title: "github.com"
    }
    summary: "The search results indicate that \"Swiggy mcp server\" refers to Swiggy\'s implementation of the Model Context Protocol (MCP), which allows AI agents (like Claude) to interact with Swiggy\'s services programmatically.\n\nHere\'s a summary of the findings:\n\n*   **Swiggy MCP Server and its Purpose:** Swiggy has launched an MCP stack, exposing multiple MCP servers for different services like Food, Instamart, and Dineout. These servers enable AI agents to perform actions such as searching restaurants, managing delivery carts, searching grocery products, and finding restaurant slots.[1] The Model Context Protocol (MCP) is an open standard that connects AI assistants to real-world data sources and services, acting as a translator between AI systems and external APIs.[2][3][4][5]\n\n*   **\"claude\\_desktop\\_config.json\":** This file is used to configure MCP clients, specifically within the Claude Desktop application.[6][2][7][4][8] It holds the configuration to connect to MCP servers, including those for Swiggy.[6][2][7] Users can manually edit this JSON file to add configurations for various MCP servers, including those that interact with services like Swiggy and Zomato.[6][7][4][8]\n\n*   **\"command\": \"npx\" OR \"node\":** The search results show that \"command\": \"npx\" is commonly used within the `mcpServers` configuration in `claude_desktop_config.json` (or similar MCP client configuration files) to run remote MCP tools.[9][10][7][4] This typically involves `npx mcp-remote` followed by the URL of the MCP server.[9][10][7][4] The use of \"node\" is also mentioned in the context of installing Node.js as a prerequisite for setting up MCP servers and for running JavaScript-based MCP server implementations.[3][4] Node.js is a runtime environment that supports various languages and is used in GitHub Actions for building, testing, and deploying applications, which could include MCP server-related projects.[11]\n\nIn essence, the query points to how AI agents are configured to interact with Swiggy\'s services (and other platforms) via the Model Context Protocol, using `claude_desktop_config.json` for configuration and `npx` or `node` for executing the necessary commands to connect to and utilize these MCP servers.\n\nSources:\n[1] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEI7K1rRKPFMyndNsnysUOKFm1mX_W3RjYazLAyzwN6Ss0mBlGVNxEBJj19wUvvYHiQoc8nykp2D_dwyaWGqiQXhz1plsQEOI8ov6qN4sGcH2wvwgqFeJrfZ48xrG75QWZJdS3z1peU4gVNiYB85iYwLOiSBNqNqOwrwkhdd0HNfpla33ZY3Zf7cjT1PXRuUuBBSDQbugGjLrzpl2KQY9Iuxa_lep3U6JJmUc9kADue_N_XqtivL_BHOu6_O0l3n-DIfpBgWOta)\n[2] [infoq.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG_HN1NQzP6cygUyeR5Q98SKD90NEAhrhBYHTDll5fhhbuXmJqYuQK_wh3zY1QqfjAnVk6vB3nEnwARFecAfICTvF3ebj-iIOGuHCI-E4IahZybQ_eR5NRQOQcHr2unC0dK91W2uZVO4-bJlXQDKSky9j44BJnkPva1kh8=)\n[3] [substack.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGLzLwHsaao9QnP_qY29js-5Ecuvz5omRwVvXHW0fNxN7JBsUMDxCY0FbpxomPs4V0iPoXjyqF5GMpRviLNz9Wv6I1p-ghtOzQMRouuMhImIOMGHOaE9q_jSy_1Sx95OWF8ZnOxxrv35l3zrzOeO-CHAuyZ6eeuBdjKWnTMGbHVTBU=)\n[4] [beehiiv.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFreyrWu6bF_zd4i-2sJ-SAazgP8wL_1n4v50NkoGnszf9jfYEuA-Vsna7VrukfZTdkgdOJafKpxIOEIMr4x-T2D58-SwWawA8-SpsOvkcrtMju3mYO6gQL9847KZmujM38a8gTZxsaRhIcHYWCChgtzx2K25InOBfpEJIp4oRLqRqHko1VrwEyZ0n2Ig==)\n[5] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIVly-pVUgwgSOfpF_Eyur9U-Vbsbs5F1fKWw8fEHBtVLe9MbddMOljZt9aXi95lIiHPZj5uLNyvg-Jr5Tdxgpw9F-e2WCkQt-nf-e1Vxcs2FbjNUpDo3IASGXvaH9oHnK2Qm3bKG_0FIUAsXpExwv9pp_3nrIULn8aVHYDQNSRSrAUZhHZYvdqIES0iTdTlGMrejhTzb26f4AYYZlxbgiV89LsudUQQ==)\n[6] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHQqr0m5PQj8inzGbdxsQYeAUhoK7MslHqwOGqM6xCLc4PhFwHlynfKRxRv3XKJtrliJ9n8acMpFz-D7y5lHWu3gS8Ti0IdOI-Vwl-nRZB7OG9TRaEEtGT2PtlryFbQrWiw3wgHHyfCdzRboAf7mlgWXw2v70t0URBAoNz