          text: "*   **Outcome**: PantryPal provides detailed recipes for the entire menu and a consolidated \"Minimal Grocery List\" with direct links to Swiggy Instamart/Zomato Blinkit, and an automated prompt for **Swiggy MCP-enabled AI systems** to autonomously order the exact missing ingredients in seconds."
